    "SSRewardText": "You pour the barrels into the subterranean river and quickly notice the pollutive effect of the strange purple liquid they contained: blind fish quickly bubble to the surface, their scales visibly corroding as they writhe in agony. Well done.\n\nAs you ponder your actions, you give your reflection in the purple water a good, hard look: a tiny shimmer in the water builds to a large glow as the biggest fish you've ever seen leaps out of the water.
